Package: GenomicState
Title: Build and access GenomicState objects for use with derfinder tools from
    sources like Gencode
Version: 0.99.13
Date: 2020-12-17
Authors@R: 
    person("Leonardo", "Collado-Torres", role = c("aut", "cre"), 
